article_title: Walgreens To Open New Clinics Staffed, Owned By Hospital Partners

article_metadata.description: In a new twist on its retail health clinic model, Walgreens Boots Alliance (WBA) says it will open up to 25 new retail clinics in Oregon and Washington states that will be owned and operated by a Seattle-based health system. The collaboration calls for Walgreens’ partner, Providence Health & Services, a [...]
